                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Apple Braille' fontsize='10'>- UK accounts for 83% of total revenue (£7.3M)</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Apple Braille' fontsize='10'>- November 2011 showed highest monthly revenue</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Apple Braille' fontsize='10'>- VIP customers (10+ orders, £2000+ spend) drive 50.9% of revenue</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Apple Braille' fontsize='10'>- B2B Model: Weekend sales low, Thursday peak</run>
