                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Apple Braille' fontsize='10'>- Stable Economics: £500-700 average order value throughout period</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Apple Braille' fontsize='10'>- Top Product: PAPER CRAFT, LITTLE BIRDIE</run>
